"""Test that Sobol is used if no GenerationStrategy is provided and
        the search space is discrete.
        """
ax_client = AxClient()
ax_client.create_experiment(parameters=[{'name': 'x', 'type': 'choice',
    'values': [1, 2, 3]}, {'name': 'y', 'type': 'choice', 'values': [1, 2, 3]}]
    )
self.assertEqual([s.model for s in not_none(ax_client.generation_strategy).
    _steps], [Models.SOBOL])
self.assertEqual(ax_client.get_max_parallelism(), [(-1, -1)])
self.assertTrue(ax_client.get_trials_data_frame().empty)
